<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Welcome to ArchKalinga</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f0f4f8;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      color: #1e293b;
    }

    p {
      color: #334155;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #1e3a5f;
      padding: 28px 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .header p {
      margin: 6px 0 0;
      color: #93c5fd;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 32px;
    }

    .content p {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin: 0 0 18px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #2563eb;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 15px;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .divider {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      margin: 28px 0;
    }

    .footer {
      padding: 20px 24px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      color: #64748b;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .content, .header, .footer {
        padding: 16px;
      }

      .button {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ArchKalinga</h1>
      <p>Project &amp; Architecture Management</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi {{data.firstName}},</p>
      <p>Welcome to <strong>ArchKalinga</strong> — your workspace for managing projects, tasks, change requests, and team collaboration in one place.</p>
      <p>Your account has been created with the email <strong>{{data.email}}</strong>. You can now log in to your dashboard and start building.</p>

      <a href="{{data.clientUrl}}/auth/login" target="_blank" class="button">Go to Dashboard →</a>

      <hr class="divider" />
      <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #94a3b8; margin: 0;">If you didn't create an ArchKalinga account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      © {{data.year}} ArchKalinga. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
